columnConfigurations.columnName: Delivery created after planned material availability date (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: Delivery created after planned material availability date (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time to Delivery item creation (days)",
	"Sales order items rejected (%)",
    "Items released by credit representative (%)",
    "Delivery created after planned material availability date (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items created") 
        	AS "Time to Delivery item creation (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Sales order items rejected")*100
        	AS "Sales order items rejected (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Items released by credit representative")*100
        	AS "Items released by credit representative (%)",
         AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery created after planned material availability date")*100
        	AS "Delivery created after planned material availability date (%)"    
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
